        "section_tag": "THE SOLUTION",
        "section_title": "What Filtered Water Actually Does",
        "section_subtitle": "We're not claiming to reverse menopause. Here's what a shower filter can and cannot do — honestly.",
        "can_title": "✓ What ShowerEnvy Can Do",
        "cannot_title": "✗ What ShowerEnvy Cannot Do",
